.\" ==================================================================
.Sh NAME
.Nm pkgman-ls
.Nd print out a listing of the package's directory
.\" ==================================================================
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm pkgman
.Cm ls
.Op Fl \-path
.Ar pkgname ...
.\" ==================================================================
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Prints out a listing of the package's directory from the packages
sources.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl \-path
Show path info.
.El
.\" ==================================================================
.Sh EXIT STATUS
0 if success, 255 if package source is not found.
